header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - Hemisfair Region - 1st Round

videos.headline: South Carolina's Beal gets a block at the rim
videos.description: Brea Beal misses her 3-point attempt, but she gets back up and chases down Shannon Titus to swat her shot out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (South Carolina's Beal gets a block at the rim) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Neal-Tysor inches Mercer closer to South Carolina's lead
videos.description: Amoria Neal-Tysor sneaks in with a steal then hustles back to drop in a fast-break layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Neal-Tysor inches Mercer closer to South Carolina's lead) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: SC's Boston ends the half with a deep 3
videos.description: Aliyah Boston drains a deep 3-pointer as time winds down in the second quarter to extend South Carolina's lead over Mercer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (SC's Boston ends the half with a deep 3) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boston shows toughness with and-1 bucket
videos.description: Aliyah Boston takes a few hits but won't be stopped as she manages to finish the shot for a chance at a 3-point play for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Boston shows toughness with and-1 bucket) 2021/03/21 ESHEET
